eplyTime":"2020-11-16T05:07:31.000Z","msg":"所以應該去個旅行,散個心先............<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b2f1d7ba60bd60702257428623f057ad296c13c","tid":2287737,"uid":340040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"170a90cd024e7ff2f79578dd705fab425b157c58","tid":2287737,"uid":54517,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"afec106ac6d35f79f9b81833eaaf9f6f6f2310d3","tid":2287737,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6924590c6717af99b206a1ac4743e57687a6e75c","tid":2287737,"uid":21028,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T04:11:32.000Z","msg":"準備睇上訴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T04:33:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T05:07:31.000Z","msg":"所以應該去個旅行,散個心先............<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T05:18:29.000Z","msg":"仲要快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8234fe22160a057a8d6812656f3b195b923be043","tid":2287737,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T06:33:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/11320\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F11320&d=fL1pPRntFf1zvvLBqslw3tKNpY%2BoLPIqDl3on0Jjdx4%3D&h=b9809df9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/11320</a><br />\n<br />\n裁決理由：<br />\n<br />\n裁判官指出本案有4個重點：<br />\n<br />\n📌涉案物品在法律條文能否介定為可以作非法用途的工具：<br />\n<br />\n由於此項涉及解讀大量復雜法律條文及終審法院案例，所以不會在此論述。<br />\n<br />\n結論：在本案中，控方不能把法律所寫的3種非法用途再作擴闊。<br />\n<br />\n📌PW1證供是否可靠：<br />\n<br />\n裁判官裁定PW1是可靠證人。他的作供合情合理，實話實說。(例如：表示不知道為何西裝男與被告糾纏，不知道當時西洋菜南街街頭的情況等)<br />\n<br />\n📌 DW1證供是否可靠：<br />\n<br />\n裁判官裁定DW1 是可靠證人。她/他的作供合情合理，實話實說。(例如：如實指出他/她與被告工作時所需的工具，指出不知道為何被告會在那時會身處旺角等)<br />\n<br />\n📌被告會否使用涉案物品作非法用途？<br />\n<br />\n裁判官裁定被告當時𢹂帶涉案物品是被告的工作需要。她認為尼龍魚絲不是用作束縛人身，六角匙不是用作偷竊用(這是從要點1得出的結論)，而鎅刀、剪刀及螺絲批則因為沒有改裝或是特製，不能排除被告是用這些用具作合法用途。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官指出即使被告當時身穿黑色裝束，現場有大量黑衣人奔跑，帶𢹂生理鹽水有可疑之處，但是由於她背包內的物品已被裁定是作合法用途，因此亦不能排除她帶𢹂生理鹽水也是作合法用途。<br />\n<br />\n最後裁判官指出被告在本案中的逃跑行為可能是有清白的原因(例如是擺脫與西裝男的糾纏)。<br />\n<br />\n因此，裁判官指因為控方未能舉證至毫無合理疑點，裁定被告罪名不成立🥳<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n按：在裁判官宣判被告罪名不成立後，庭內歡喜若狂😆最後感謝旁聽人士沒有聽完一單就走，庭內幾乎滿座💛"},{"pid":"53da7732822e34a4edb4bbedf7166571cfec3714","tid":2287737,"uid":66536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bde07c7630efab93cadc6a960c38b780f0b10c0d","tid":2287737,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c7f212ff470086ceb081afef63fef7d31c18741","tid":2287737,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8871a5ab027bdd010caa506b0596d401b402dad9","tid":2287737,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T04:15:26.000Z","msg":"劉官都唔入 就真係好𨳊嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T04:39:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T04:44:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T06:38:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7dfbc5f6556ef20c144bd334b5f8009bd412fe5","tid":2287737,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T06:38:40.000Z","msg":"依單好彩，俾紅官審死硬。<br />\n<br />\n完了，手足快Ｄ去散心，唔好遲啦"},{"pid":"5c7fce3463d62779b0bc444448544b69d93feb77","tid":2287737,"uid":110043